# =============================================================================
# Rust build output
# =============================================================================
/target
debug/
**/*.rs.bk
*.pdb

# Cargo.lock committed for workspace (contains both lib and potential bin crates)
# This ensures reproducible builds across development machines.
# For library-only crates, crates.io ignores Cargo.lock anyway.

